message.body: Hey Britt. Are we still on tonight?
Yeah I believe so. The movie is at 7:45, and it's about two hours long. So it'll be done around 10, then I'll text you and let you know where I'm at. You
'll need to send me an address
Sweet
Ok. Any plans on where to go? I know mad river in manayunk has some sort of July 4th party tonight
I'd rather just go around my house. A million bars by me. Kind of a hassle for me to get to manayunk
If that's cool
Yeah that's fine. I just didn't know what you were up for. Plus I dunno much about your area
I live in center city practically. Two blocks from art museum. I mean I'm even down for just getting a bottle or wine or something and hanging out at my place
I can go out too though. Dun matter
Ok, well I'll leave the plan up to you. I'm down for anything
I feel like since u will most likely be getting here late we probably wouldn't get out til kinda late. Might be better to just chill at my house. We can always just play it by ear too
Ok sounds good to me. We'll see what you feel up to doing tonight
What do u like to drink?
I'm a girl.... So girly shit of course. Anything with vodka and fruit juice lol.
I don't drink much wine, so I dunno about that
Like I dunno what I would like in terms of wine
OK i like vodka too. I got some grey goose at my house I need to finish!!
Looks like we got ourselves a plan now lol
Yea I can't wait til work is over and my vacation begins!!!
Looks like we got ourselves a plan now lol
Me too! I'm done at 4 today :) be jealous
I'm done then everyday! Hahahaha
Fuck. Hahahah I hate you
my bad. U usually done at 5?
Yeah
If u pass by a wawa or somethin on Ur way here can u pick up some juice? I have some but not sure if its enough
Ok I will. Movie just ended
Sweet. U coming straight here?
Yeah I think so
Getting off 76
On 23rd st?
The highway
Where do I park?
Idk. I think my street is blocked off. Do u want me to come out?
happy 4th of July!!
Happy 4th! You make it to the beach ok?
Haha yea. Did u have an OK time last night
Yeah it was good. I just felt weird cuz you got a little drunk, or maybe alot drunk and I felt awkward taking advantage of you like I planned on after th
e "you always come over when you break up with someone" talk
Haha u took that heart huh?
Yeah you said it enough
Well u gotta come over other times. That's all lol
Hahah I guess so
Did that make u mad or something?
It wasn't exactly a happy comment
I'm sorry I didn't mean to offend u
It's ok. It's whatever
man I feel bad. I didn't think it was that bad. :-(
Hahha you're fine
We never gonna see each other again?
I didn't say that. We can
